claim: Outkast is composed of two people.
premise_source_doc_sentence: Outkast  (  stylized as OutKast  )  is an American hip hop duo formed in 1991 , in East Point , Atlanta , Georgia , composed of Atlanta-based rappers André `` André 3000 '' Benjamin  (  formerly known as Dré  )  and Antwan `` Big Boi '' Patton .
